long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Just Launched is a Chrome extension that monitors the major product launch sites so you don't have to. When a brand new product is launched, be the first to be notified.

Product Hunt, Beta List, Show Hacker News and more.

Never miss a product launch again.

Data taken from http://www.launchfeed.com/
